book.13.content.page0:
My name is Ehrendil Morvaris...
I am a researcher about a phenomenon that we all named Kal'amath...
We don't know how it got here and how to make it go away.
It started as a small infected area in our  undergrounds.
When I inspected a sample of this...
book.13.content.page1: ... uncanny thing it turned out to be highly organic. We assume it came in through abandoned sewers...  We watched this specimen for several days, it was growing very quickly and we are still not sure what it was feeding on...
book.13.content.page2:
after some time, some units started to disappear unexpectedly, a trip to the underground was organized, where we saw a completely infected space.
The atmosphere in the underground changed unable to be fixed and the passage to sewage was ordered to be closed...
book.13.content.page3:
...for safety reasons.
We still don't know what condition the basement is in now. I guess we wouldn't want to know because it might be too much of a threat..

The research was officially discontinued

book.17.content.page0: I saw something I should not have... Everything around me was red, and I saw something that looked like an eye, I don't even know how I got to this place, but I was quickly caught by the guards. Later, the entrance was blocked so no one would find out about
book.17.content.page1:
the existence of this creature.
Now I will spend the rest of my life surrounded by gray bricks and memories about this mystery, that is The Eye for me...
             -Gwythyr
book.17.title: Eye
book.19.content.page0:
Dear Father,
I am close to achieving our destiny.
Tonight, The Darkness will consume the lands of our people.
You and mother would be proud of me.
Soon, we will meet again...

book.23.content.page0:
For years, there has been a prophecy that the royal family received from a mysterious fortune teller at the birth of our young ruler

 Caranthir von der  Laethyr...
book.23.content.page1:
The fortune read: 

Three worthy rulers, should lay down their skulls as they lay their bodies to sleep.
The sand of the souls of our ancestors will accept our gifts, and the world will be swallowed by darkness and gloom.
book.23.content.page2:
When the family heard the fortune, they fell into despair. Their son's entire life had a single goal that was inevitable. 

In front of the castle, the skulls of our rulers and the souls of the people are waiting for their final farewell...
book.23.title: Prophecy

book.26.content.page0:
....if you're reading this, I'm probably not here anymore... I managed to escape from the prison. I was smart, of course, until he sensed me, they're looking for me. 
I don't know how to hide from the guards anymore.
book.26.content.page1:
He knew that I knew what they were planning, 

The skeletons have something that could cover the world in darkness forever...

Whoever is reading this, please don't let the King fulfill his destiny...

The day of Darkness is approaching...

                -Gwythyr
